{"type":"message","id":"1cc03cbd","parentId":"03c0c200","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:04:50.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the iCloud emails more carefully. I see 4 emails in iCloud. Let me check which ones are new (unread). The \"!\" flag means urgent/flagged, \"R\" means read. Let me read the unread ones and all 4 to be thorough.\n\nAlso let me read the Gmail email more carefully - just 1 new one from Google Cloud.\n\nLet me read the iCloud emails to get summaries.","thinkingSignature":"05710f861890092aeed2728304f0b4a4b18fe1f247ee5774426459e2a745b7f6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aioosj0manwl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 9 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aioosj0manwl_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 8 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1033,"output":181,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20250,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777345484991,"responseId":"063f56cdde16ab6f1882ade7630f8a7e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3288a7f","parentId":"1cc03cbd","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:04:52.758Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aioosj0manwl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1351,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777345492758}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4686418","parentId":"e3288a7f","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:04:52.759Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aioosj0manwl_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2103,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777345492758}}
{"type":"message","id":"c8a25262","parentId":"e4686418","timestamp":"2026-04-28T03:05:04.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compile the results.\n\n**Gmail:**\n1 new email - Google Cloud product update about OpenTelemetry - LOW PRIORITY\n\n**iCloud:**\n4 emails total. Let me check which are new (not yet read by me in this session). Looking at the flags:\n- Email 9: No flags (unread) - from RC Leasing about apartment, IMPORTANT\n- Email 8: \"! R\" - flagged and read - RC Leasing about apartment, seems older\n- Email 7: \"R\" - read - older\n- Email 6: \"R\" - read - older\n\nSo only email 9 is truly new/unread. The others are already read. Let me send the two messages.\n\n\nActually, I'm noticing email 8 has that \"!\" flag which typically means urgent or flagged in himalaya, but it's marked as read. Since the question specifically asks about new iCloud emails and email 8 is already read, I'll focus on the unread ones for the new count.","thinkingSignature":"77458609fd1a0c07a2d60796f511df4caa7fb82e7b0c9e7b21b4e8fa3f9c4267"},{"type":"text","text":"📬 GMAIL — New Mail (1 new)\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• Google Cloud — [Product Update] Automatic enablement of new OpenTelemetry ingestion API\n  └ Google Cloud announced automatic enablement of a new OpenTelemetry ingestion API — no action needed\n\n---\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sxzizypsl9do_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"8212808444","message":"📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (1 new)\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• RC Leasing (Amy Smith) — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ Amy says she may have a unit for your timeframe, first come first serve — waiting on Logan to complete his application before running apps"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1515,"output":383,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20934,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"t